overview.welcome.message: Welcome to the documentation of the interactive statistics learning environment (ISLE) and the ISLE Editor for authoring interactive lessons for statistics and related disciplines. One of our aims is to encourage instructors at universities and other learning institutions to use it for their purposes. For questions, please contact us via email at pgb AT andrew.cmu.edu.
